OL,6,FSalford Red Devils have secured their
OL,7,Ffuture following a takeover by
OL,8,Fbusinessman on the eve of the Rugby
OL,9,FSuper League.
OL,11,FThe club's new owner Dario Berta, who
OL,12,Fis leading a consortium, completed a
OL,13,Ffull purchase and promised significant
OL,14,Finvestment.
OL,16,FIts future was in serious doubt over
OL,17,Fthe winter after talks with a previous
OL,18,Fconsortium stalled, which led to many
OL,19,Fof their star players being placed on
OL,20,Fthe transfer list.
