OL,6,FSalford were handed a sustainability
OL,7,Fsalary cap of #1.2m and ordered to
OL,8,Fsell players by the Rugby Football
OL,9,FLeague in January 2025.
OL,11,FThe new owners have already made their
OL,12,Ffirst appointment, with former Chief
OL,13,FCommercial Officer at Salford Red
OL,14,FDevils Chris Irwin appointed as the
OL,15,Fclub's new Chief Executive Officer.
OL,17,FIn a statement on Friday, 7 February,
OL,18,FDario Berta, said: "This is the start
OL,19,Fof a very bright and successful future
OL,20,Ffor Salford Red Devils.
