OL,6,FSalford City Mayor Paul Dennett added:
OL,7,F"I'm very happy to welcome Dario Berta
OL,8,Fto Salford and look forward to working
OL,9,Fclosely together to see an exciting
OL,10,Ffuture for Salford Red Devils,
OL,11,Fbuilding on the successes of the last
OL,12,Ffive years."
OL,14,FThe takeover comes on the eve of the
OL,15,FRugby Super League season, which
OL,16,Fbegins on Friday, 7 February.
OL,17,FSalford's first match is on on
OL,18,FSaturday, 15 February, away to St
OL,19,FHelens.
